{"tid":1921250,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"NBA to suspend season following Wednesday's games","createTime":"2020-03-12T01:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T01:49:39.000Z","uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"286a8382acba4b4a341e52a2b11147f28750e0e3","tid":1921250,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:41:19.000Z","msg":"NBA to suspend season following Wednesday's games<br />\nOfficial release<br />\nMar 11, 2020 9:37 PM ET<br />\n<br />\nNEW YORK -- The NBA announced that a player on the Utah Jazz has preliminarily tested positive for COVID-19.  The test result was reported shortly prior to the tip-off of tonight&rsquo;s game between the Jazz and Oklahoma City Thunder at Chesapeake Energy Arena.  At that time, tonight&rsquo;s game was canceled.  The affected player was not in the arena.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nba.com/article/2020/03/11/nba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nba.com%2Farticle%2F2020%2F03%2F11%2Fnba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lYHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=336380d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nba.com/article/2020/03/11/nba-suspend-season-following-wednesdays-games</a>"},{"pid":"817c133bb3feb4609344d8d273515891e8b7f70b","tid":1921250,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:41:58.000Z","msg":"The NBA is suspending game play following the conclusion of tonight&rsquo;s schedule of games until further notice.  The NBA will use this hiatus to determine next steps for moving forward in regard to the coronavirus pandemic."},{"pid":"11fcce0848633a809976b0af9891b36eeb91db19","tid":1921250,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾玖期牆紙】 兄弟爬山<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1919455/page